{"fields":{"body":[{"value":"In our race toward modernity, amid all the technological innovation and the rapid growth of our cities,  silence is now quickly passing into legend. Beginning with an ode to John Cage’s seminal silent composition 4’33”, the sights and sounds of this film delicately interweave with silence to create a contemplative and cinematic experience that works its way through frantic minds and into the quiet spaces of hearts.\r\n \r\nAs much a work of devotion as it is a documentary, In  Pursuit  of  Silence is a meditative exploration of our relationship with silence, sound, and the impact of noise on our lives.","format":1}],"teaser":[{"value":"A meditative film about our relationship with silence, sound, and the impact of noise.","format":1}],"series_nid":[{"nid":null}],"season":[{"value":null}],"episode":[{"value":null}],"instructor":[{"value":null}],"director":[{"value":"Patrick Shen"}],"producer":[{"value":"Patrick Shen, Andrew Brumme, Brandon Vedder"}],"writer":[{"value":null}],"cast":[{"value":"Greg Hindy, Pico Iyer, John Cage, Helen Lees, George Prochnik, Roshi Gensho Hozumi"}],"copyright":[{"value":"2016"}],"studio":[{"value":"Transcendental Media"}],"video_lang":[{"value":"English"}]},"drupal_cache":"not-drupal","nid":178606,"type":"product_video","language":"en","primaryLanguage":"en","cta":{"label":null,"path":null,"deeplinkPath":null},"title":"In Pursuit of Silence","promote":0,"status":1,"comment_count":8,"created":1541037600,"is_new":false,"path":"video/pursuit-silence","seo":{"title":"In Pursuit of Silence","description":"A meditative film about our relationship with silence, sound, and the","robots":{"noIndex":false,"noFollow":false}},"product_type":"single","display_type":"normal","admin_category":{"tid":26611,"vid":12,"name":"Personal Growth","weight":0},"site_segment":{"id":120011,"name":"Transformation"},"visual_interest_image":{"visual_interest_xl":null},"coverart_image":{"hdtv_190x266":"https://brooklyn.gaia.com/v1/image-ren